promoterAddress: 305, Mauryansh Elanza, Near Parekh Hospital Shyamal Cross Road, Satellite,Ahmedabad Ahmedabad 380015

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1)The unsecured Loan details has been taken from the books as on 28/01/2022 however we have relied on the management
confirmation for such unsecured loan Balance.
2) The construction cost incurred and paid by the Promoter is  more than 27 crore but the utility of Form 3 does not allow to show cost incurred and paid more than the cost estimate and hence construction cost incurred and paid is shown as per the estimated cost.
3)As per information and explanation provided to us and based on our verification, there are no encumbrances created on any
unit by promoter as on the date of this certificate
4)We have relied on the work of an expert who has issued Form 1 and Form 2 while determining the project completion status
and cost incurred for such project.
5) it is the responsibility of the management to include PAN and Mobile no of prospective buyer and we have relied on the details
provided by the promoter of the firm.
6) At the time of estimation of Finance cost for the project, Interest on partners capital was included in Estimated finance cost however as per ICAI Guidelines, Interest on Partners capital is not to be considered as cost of Development and hence the same has been excluded from Interest on Money borrowed for Construction.
7) As per information and explanation provided to us, Promoter had made a call  to allottee to come for an agreement to sale however some of them could not appear for registration due to corona pendamic and the same is pending for registration.
8) The amount withdrawn from RERA Designated Account includes amount withdrawn from members who have cancelled the unit after making booking with promoter of the firm.
9) Promoter had received BU permission on 14-09-2020 . Hence, promtoer is making direct sale deed with allottees who had booked units after the date of BU permission which is a violation of the provision of section 13 of the RERA Act.
10) The promoter of the project has made handover the project with Service society created under the law. the Amount to be deposited into RERA Account is shown at 100 percent but there is no need of such transfer as the project is completed and construction cost pending to be incurred is the estimated cost which is not required to be incurred now.
